+//! Flesch Reading Ease — SF parity.
+//!
+//! Formula (verbatim from Screaming Frog's `seospider/id694424387.java`):
+//!
+//!     score = clamp(206.835 - 1.015 * (words/sentences) - 84.6 * (syllables/words), 0, 100)
+//!
+//! Higher score = easier to read. The seven buckets match SF's enum.
