+SF runs LanguageTool *locally* via `org.languagetool.JLanguageTool`. Options for Rust:
+- Run bundled LT JAR via subprocess (heavy)
+- HTTP to public LT API (rate-limited, external dep)
+- Native Rust grammar checker — no mature option exists
+
+This slice is XL and will need its own brainstorming round. Out of scope for sub-project 2's first pass.
