+## Slice 2.8 — LLM embeddings (future PR)
+
+Depends on slice 5.6 (AI provider abstraction). Embeds page text via configured provider, computes cosine sim across all pairs.
+
+Thresholds (from SF `EmbeddingsConfig`): 0.95 for `CONTENT_COSINE_SIMILARITY`, 0.40 for `CONTENT_LOW_RELEVANCE` (vs anchor prompt).
