+## Goal
+
+Bring this Rust workspace to behavioral parity with Screaming Frog SEO Spider's 33 tabs and their underlying algorithms, while keeping the SaaS shape (multi-tenant Postgres + Redis + Axum API + React UI) we already chose over SF's single-user Derby desktop architecture.
